<section id="venue" class="level2 web">
<h2 class="web">Venue</h2>
<figure>
<img src="/tali_map.png" alt="The tournament venue" />
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">The tournament venue</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>The tournament courts are located in the Tali Sports Park. See the
map above for entrance instructions. There is a <strong>water
point</strong> next to the lunch tent, but the only <strong>toilets are
in the changing rooms</strong>, a 200 meters walk from the courts.</p>
<p>The address is: Purotie 8, 00380 Helsinki, Finland</p>
<ul>
<li><a
href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&amp;query=60.2128,24.8700">Google
Maps</a></li>
<li><a
href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/?mlat=60.2128&amp;mlon=24.8700#map=17/60.2128/24.8700">OpenStreetMap</a></li>
</ul>
<p>If you arrive by car, there is a spacious parking lot right next to
the venue. You need to install the ParkMan app to pay for the
parking.</p>
</section>
