<section id="preplay-friday" class="level3">
<h3>Preplay Friday</h3>
<p>The preplay takes place on <strong>Friday 24th July from 2pm to 6pm
at Savela Frisbee Park</strong> (note: not the tournament venue). We’ll
set up around four courts to warm up for the weekend.</p>
<p>The address is: Lucina Hagmanin polku 2, 00710 Helsinki</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/T6SqVpBeL32HLYou6">Google
Maps</a></li>
<li><a
href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/search?lat=60.237862&amp;lon=24.994969&amp;zoom=17#map=17/60.237862/24.994969">OpenStreetMap</a></li>
</ul>
<figure>
<img src="/savela_map.png" alt="Savela Frisbee Park map" />
<figcaption aria-hidden="true">Savela Frisbee Park map</figcaption>
</figure>
<p>Easiest way to get there is to ride a train to the Pukinmäki station,
take the southern exit from the station, turn left after the ramp to the
underpass, and then walk straight for 5 minutes. Tram 15 stops also
nearby, there’s a 15 minute walk through the suburb of Pihlajisto, and
the forest park of Rapakivenpuisto.</p>
</section>
